  "bezeichnung": "SE Practices 1",
  "kreditpunkte": 4,
  "lernziele": "<p>All participants are able to explain and apply selected software engineering practices effectively, using modern state-of-the-art methods and tools.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Selected practices from the following disciplines will be covered:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Business modelling</li>\n<li>Requirements</li>\n<li>Analysis and design</li>\n<li>Verification</li>\n<li>Deployment</li>\n<li>Configuration and change management</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The taxonomy and format of the Unified Process (UP) and the Unified Modelling Language (UML) will be used whenever appropriate.</p>",
  "vorausgKenntnisse": "<p>Englische Sprachkenntnisse</p>\n<p>(Dieses Modul wird auf Englisch durchgef&uuml;hrt.)</p>",
